text: Santa Margarita ("Saint Margaret") may refer to: *Santa Margarita (shipwreck), a shipwreck off the coast of Florida near Key West ;Places *Santa Margarita, Mosta, Malta *Santa Margarita Island, Magdalena Bay, Baja California Sur, Mexico *Santa Margarita, Samar, Philippines *Santa Margarita, Trinidad and Tobago *Santa Margarita, California, United States *Rancho Santa Margarita, California, United States **Santa Margarita Catholic High School, a private, Catholic high school in Rancho Santa Margarita == See also == * Margarita * Saint Margaret (disambiguation) * Santa Margherita (disambiguation)
title: Santa Margarita
